These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, helicopter
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person driving the helicopter##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | helicopter   | snowmobile  |
| Sport   | soccer | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lemon
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apple | lemon      |
| Pet    | pall-mall  | bluemaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, pumpkin
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | pumpkin  | plum    |
| Sport   | balloon-flower | bellflower |

