.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, folk
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the fan folk is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the fan folk is somewhere to the right of the fan disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | disco  | folk |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, photography
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | hiking  | photography |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf      |

